{{!
    @template core_course/archive_progress_no_progress_recorded

    This template generates a confirmation page to archive course progress of users.

    Classes required for JS:
    * none

    Data attributes required for JS:
    * none

    Context variables required for this template:
    * heading string title to display
    * message string message displayed when there's no progress to reset
    * button string button to redirect the user back

    Other context variables for following partials:
     * core_course/archive_progress_conflict_list

    Example context (json):
    {
        "heading": "hello",
        "message": "No progress yet",
        "linked_progs_certs": [],
        "button": "/site/course.php"
    }
}}

<h2>{{{heading}}}</h2>
<br>
{{#linked_progs_certs}}
  {{> core_course/archive_progress_conflict_list }}
{{/linked_progs_certs}}
{{^linked_progs_certs}}
  {{{message}}}
{{/linked_progs_certs}}

<br><br><br>
{{{button}}}
